Pre-installation Instructions
=============================

The following programs and libraries are required to run IsoXpressor:

python 2.7
libgd 
giflib 
gdmodule 
Pillow 
matplotlib 
biopython 
numpy

These can be installed on Ubuntu using:

 $ sudo apt-get install libgd-dev libgif-dev

and

 $ sudo apt-get install python-gd python-imaging python-matplotlib python-biopython python-numpy


To install IsoXpressor simply run the following command from within the downloaded IsoXpressor directory.


 $ ./pre-install.sh 
 

Basic Instructions
==================

After installation you can call IsoXpressor from this directory via

 $ python IsoXpressor.py -h
